    <h3>Research Papers</h3>
    <p>The papers below are also available in a <a
            href="https://www.cs.cornell.edu/home/kleinber/chrono.html">chronological list</a>Additional bibliographic
        information can be found at <a href="https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/k/Kleinberg:Jon_M=.html">DBLP</a>and <a
            href="http://scholar.google.com/citations?user=VX7d5EQAAAAJ&hl=en&oi=ao">Google Scholar</a></p>
    </p>
